skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: skip count
des: Skip Count is a simple and interactive Alexa skill aimed at making learning to skip count fun. Skill helps reinforce the concept of counting from 1 to 100 and also count in increments. Safe and Suitable for children and adults of any age. No personal information collected by the skill.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
